<p>Smith, F.&nbsp;B.&nbsp;(1982). <em>Florence Nightingale: Reputation and Power</em>. Croon Helm, London <span class="MATH"><img align="bottom" alt="$ \&amp;$" border="0" height="17" src="http://encyclopedia-dev.springerwiki.com/cache/objects/78/l2h/img12.png" title="$ \&amp;$" width="19" /></span> Canberra.</p>
