<dd>van der Waerden, B.L. (1968). Mendel's experiments. <i>Centaurus</i>, <b>12</b>, 275-288.<br />
<br />
<br />
<p>Oscar Sheynin</p>
</dd>
</dl>
<p><br /></p>
