<p>Pearson, Karl, (1914-1930). <i>The Life, Letters and Labours of Francis Galton</i>. 3 vol. in 4 parts, Cambridge University Press, Cambridge.</p>
<p>Porter, Theodore M. (1986). <i>The Rise of Statistical Thinking. 1820-1900</i>. Princeton Univ. Press, Princeton.</p>
<p>Semmel, Barnard. (1958). Karl Pearson: Socialist and Darwinist. <i>British Journal of Sociology</i>, <b>9</b>, 111-125.</p>
<p>Stigler, Steven M. (1986). <i>The History of Statistics: The Measurement of Uncertainty before 1900.</i> Belknap Press of Harvard University Press, Cambridge, MA.<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<p>Eileen Magnello</p>
<p><br /></p>
