<dt><a name="2">2</a></dt>
<dd>Seng, Y.P. (1951). Historical survey of the development of sampling theories and practice. <i>Journal of the Royal Statistical Society Series A</i>, <b>114</b>, 214-231.<br />
<br />
<br />
<p>Ib Thomsen</p>
</dd>
</dl>
