<dd>ifc Bulletin: Bulletin of the Irving Fisher Committee on Central-Bank Statistics.</dd>
<dt><a name="8">8</a></dt>
<dd>Kenessey, Z. (1997). The significance of Fisher's ideas for National Accounts, in ifc Bulletin, No. 1, November 1997.</dd>
<dt><a name="9">9</a></dt>
<dd>Vogt, A. and Barta, B. (1997). <i>The Making of Tests for Index Numbers. Mathematical Methods of Descriptive Statistics</i>, Published in Honour of the 50th Anniversary of the Death of Irving Fisher, Physica-Verlag, Heidelberg.<br />
<br />
<br />
<p>A. Vogt</p>
</dd>
</dl>
