<dd>Badey,L. (1929). Buffon, précurseur de la science démographique. <i>Annales de géographie,</i> May, 206-220.</dd>
<dt><a name="2">2</a></dt>
<dd>Buffon, G.L., (1749-1804). <i>Histoire naturelle, générale et particulière</i>, 44 volumes, Imprimerie Royale [later Plassan], Paris. [This is the original complete edition. The most authoritative subsequent edition is that published in 1884-1885 (14 volumes in-8), annotated and preceded by an introduction by J.L. Lanessan, followed by the general correspondence of Buffon, collected and annotated by Nadault de Buffon, Librairie A. Le Vasseur, Paris,].</dd>
