<dt><a name="11">11</a></dt>
<dd>Hald, A. (1998). <i>A History of Mathematical Statistics from 1750 to 1930</i>, Wiley, New York. See also the contributions of Helmert (1872), Plackett (1972), Seal (1967) and Sprott (1978) referenced therein.</dd>
<dt><a name="12">12</a></dt>
